socdom_1: Show how much you agree or disagree with each idea below by selecting a number from 1 to 5 on the scale below. You can work quickly; your first feeling is generally best. - Group equality should not be our primary goal.
socdom_2: Show how much you agree or disagree with each idea below by selecting a number from 1 to 5 on the scale below. You can work quickly; your first feeling is generally best. - It is unjust to try to make groups equal.
socdom_3: Show how much you agree or disagree with each idea below by selecting a number from 1 to 5 on the scale below. You can work quickly; your first feeling is generally best. - We should do what we can to equalize conditions for different groups.
socdom_4: Show how much you agree or disagree with each idea below by selecting a number from 1 to 5 on the scale below. You can work quickly; your first feeling is generally best. - We should work to give all groups an equal chance to succeed.
socdom_5: Show how much you agree or disagree with each idea below by selecting a number from 1 to 5 on the scale below. You can work quickly; your first feeling is generally best. - An ideal society requires some groups to be on top and others to be on the bottom.
socdom_6: Show how much you agree or disagree with each idea below by selecting a number from 1 to 5 on the scale below. You can work quickly; your first feeling is generally best. - Some groups of people are simply inferior to other groups.
socdom_7: Show how much you agree or disagree with each idea below by selecting a number from 1 to 5 on the scale below. You can work quickly; your first feeling is generally best. - No one group should dominate in society.
socdom_8: Show how much you agree or disagree with each idea below by selecting a number from 1 to 5 on the scale below. You can work quickly; your first feeling is generally best. - Groups at the bottom are just as deserving as groups at the top.

pic_12: To what extent would you say you agree with the following statements? - Politics and political issues just don’t impact me.

pic_15: To what extent would you say you agree with the following statements? - It is important that I obtain news about a political topic from several sources before I will talk about it with others.
